Beirut radio stations said Israelihelicopter gunships raided south Lebanon and that one of thecraft was downed.    State owned Beirut Radio quoted witnesses as saying onehelicopter was apparently shot down by heavy anti-aircraft fireas it attacked targets in the Ain al-Hilweh area east of theport of Sidon.    The Sunni Moslem Voice of the Homeland radio said thehelicopter was seen falling into the sea.    There was no immediate independent confirmation of thereports. REUTER&#3;